io.crums.sldg.entry

Packages that use io.crums.sldg.entry
Package Description
io.crums.sldg.bags
Interfaces for retrieving a information about a subset of data from a ledger.
io.crums.sldg.entry
The original content whose input hash makes it into the ledger is abstracted away here.
io.crums.sldg.packs
Implementation classes for various bags.
